version_description: The latest version of the Cineworld Cinemas app introduces several enhancements and bug fixes, including better handling of Unlimited accounts.

* Store your e-tickets in the app, no need to print or looking for emails
* Improved stability
* Login with Facebook
* Save the time directly to your calendar
